      • addInResourcesFilter

        public void addInResourcesFilter(@NonNull
                                 java.util.List<Resource> resources)
        Adds an "In" filter related to resources.

        Similar to addInDeviceIdsFilter(List) AND addInResourcePathsFilter(List).

        Warning: this filter would be verified for any resource which has a device Id and a resource path present in the pool of device ids and resource paths defined by the list of resources. Therefore, this is not exactly a filter "IN resources present in the list defined below".

        Parameters:
        resources - resources to consider.

        public SubscriptionFilterOptions notInResources(@NonNull

        Creates a "Not in" filter related to resources.

        Similar to addNotInResourcesFilter(List) *

        Equivalent to addNotInDeviceIdsFilter(List) AND addNotInResourcePathsFilter(List).

        Warning: this filter would be verified for any resource which has a device Id and a resource path which are both not present in the pool of device ids and resource paths defined by the list of resources below. Therefore, this is not exactly a filter " NOT IN resources present in the list defined below".

        Parameters:
        resources - resources to consider.
        Returns:
        this filter
